## 1) Market flow change

### Replace this:

```sql
WHERE LOCATE(CONCAT(',', CAST(t.MARKET_ID AS CHAR), ','), CONCAT(',', IN_MARKET_CSV, ',')) > 0
```

### With this:

```sql
WHERE FIND_IN_SET(CAST(t.MARKET_ID AS CHAR), IN_MARKET_CSV) > 0
```

Do this in both places:

```sql
FROM V_F_SLEEPY_CELL_4G_H t
```

and

```sql
